LINK TO CAD This water cooling system uses a distribution manifold with 9mm barb fitting tube intake and 4mm OD push-to-fit distribution ports. Same thing happens on the collector side.
The 4mmOD config was selected to match components designed by my good friend Vez.

Happy Printing
